Description: remembeep
        =========
        Simple script for plaing mp3 file periodically
        
        Install
        -------
            $ sudo aptitude install mpg123
            $ sudo pip install remembeep
        
        Usage
        -----
        Play sound every 15 minutes:
        
            $ remembeep 15
        
        Stop plaing:
        
            $ remembeep stop
        
        All options:
        
            $ remembeep -h
